_sText:
A weekend project. Started it yesterday, finished it tonight. No big project but it turned out ok.
I don't know if it has been done before, it probably has been, but this map is made fully out of cards. So no ladders, railings, boxes... just cards. A lot of cards. 
-Map built from nothing but cards
-Support up to 50 players, but that's not recommended
-Custom Textures
-Lighting with colour correction
-3d-skybox(the room)
-Joker-button. Allows one person to be teleported to the top of the middle tower
-No .nav file, bots really suck on this

Made by: SmOoth.nl
Inspiration:www.cardstacker.com (I do realise it looks nothing like what he makes)


Enjoy,

SmOoth.nl
